import { configureStore,createSlice } from "@reduxjs/toolkit";

const initTab={tbl:[{id:1,nomP:"samsung"},{id:2,nomP:"Apple"},{id:3,nomP:"xiaomi"}]}
const todoReducer=createSlice({
    name:'table',
    initialState:initTab,
    reducers:{
        Ajouter:function(state,action){
            state.tbl.push(action.payload)
         },
         
         Supremier:function(state,action){
             state.tbl=state.tbl.filter((f)=>f.id!==parseInt(action.payload))
             
         }
    }
})
export const{Ajouter,Supremier}=todoReducer.actions;

export const store=configureStore({
    reducer:{
        table:todoReducer.reducer,
    }
})
